caption:
FENTY FAM! 
Welcome to EPISODE 1: A guide to lining your lips with the new #TracedOut lipliner 🖤 

I prepped the lips with Plush Puddin in ‘Kalahari Melon’ followed by #TracedOut Pencil Lip Liner in shade ‘Riri’ 👄 

* Begin by lining the bottom centre of the lip 
* Trace out your cupids bow in whichever way it naturally curves
* Glide the liner from the corners UP to your cupids bow 
* Back to the bottom centre & up to the corners of your mouth taking the liner inside the boarder of the lip for a lift 

I sealed this look with #GlossBombStix in ‘Riri’
